#

Garlic Herb Butter Steak with Asparagus

25 min
$15
650 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeKetoPaleo

Cuisine:

AmericanSteakhouse

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

Quick MealSteakHealthyLow Carb

Description

Juicy steak seared to perfection, topped with a rich garlic herb butter, served alongside tender asparagus.

Ingredients

  • steak (ribeye or sirloin): 1 lb
  • asparagus: 1 bunch
  • butter: 1/4 cup
  • garlic (minced): 3 cloves
  • fresh parsley (chopped): 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
